{"tid":630254,"cid":25,"subCid":0,"title":"澳洲趣聞：放生唔願走　樹熊見到同伴開心齊爬樹","createTime":"2018-04-15T12:28:29.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-16T01:39:35.000Z","uid":109136,"like":13,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"17b19ce51a2dfa484310a805d8cd23e2e4a03b14","tid":630254,"uid":109136,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-15T12:28:29.000Z","msg":"真正的友誼是共同進退，在大自然也不例外。澳洲新南威爾士省一個樹熊保育組織日前把兩隻樹熊放生時，其中一隻不願離去爬回地面。當牠看到同伴爬上樹後，隨即緊隨對方的步伐，重投大自然的懷抱。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/int/bkn/cnt/news/20180413/photo/bknint-20180413180243614-0413_17011_001_01b.jpg?20180413180358\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fint%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20180413%2Fphoto%2Fbknint-20180413180243614-0413_17011_001_01b.jpg%3F20180413180358&h=0c67acb1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n職員以手輕托莫頓的尾部，鼓勵牠爬上大樹。（左圖）；莫頓（右圖右）看到希羅科爬上樹後，隨即緊隨對方的步伐。（互聯網圖片）<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n從片段可見，斯蒂芬斯港樹熊基金會（Port Stephens Koala Foundation）的職員放生樹熊莫頓（Morton）時，職員以手輕托牠的尾部，鼓勵牠爬上大樹。惟莫頓不為所動，反而逕自爬下地面。此時，另一職員打開一個被毛巾覆蓋的籠子，莫頓看見同伴希羅科（Scirocoo）後上前打招呼。當希羅科火速地爬上大樹後，莫頓亦隨即跟上，回歸大自然。<br />\n<br />\n莫頓於去年6月獲救時，體重只有344克。希羅科則是被母親遺棄，再由途人在晾衣繩上發現。基金會的職員祝願，莫頓與希羅科日後有多姿多采的野外生活。"},{"pid":"544ee5cabd4860a9911f29b90231307382ef8871","tid":630254,"uid":24730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-15T15:58:17.000Z","msg":"片呢"},{"pid":"f1a4ae45b4c8b63f105c4f18c6ab02cfb453516e","tid":630254,"uid":109136,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"544ee5cabd4860a9911f29b90231307382ef8871","tid":630254,"uid":24730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-15T15:58:17.000Z","msg":"片呢"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-16T01:38:42.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/int/bkn/cnt/news/20180413/bknint-20180413180243614-0413_17011_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fint%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20180413%2Fbknint-20180413180243614-0413_17011_001.html&d=ZwCjmBT0kzfAd9fKNb%2F40%2F%2F4Bxi6eTjWtF%2F0WJNXpvw%3D&h=05794665\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/int/bkn/cnt/news/20180413/bknint-20180413180243614-0413_17011_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"252e5f29c9dda47bbec51d2e7692a6745e0fc93c","tid":630254,"uid":11254,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-16T01:39:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://vignette.wikia.nocookie.net/evchk/images/f/f4/MnVy1.jpg/revision/latest?cb=20121107040136\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fvignette.wikia.nocookie.net%2Fevchk%2Fimages%2Ff%2Ff4%2FMnVy1.jpg%2Frevision%2Flatest%3Fcb%3D20121107040136&h=3c8662c0&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}